                      Store your converted JSON in version control systems like <strong>Git</strong>. Always commit converted files (not minified) to your repository for better code review and diff tracking. Use <code className="bg-slate-100 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">.prettierrc</code> or <code className="bg-slate-100 px-2 py-0.5 rounded">.editorconfig</code> to enforce consistent formatting across your team.
